snippet.title: [PRINCESS CLOSET] REO WALKTHROUGH - CHAPTER ONE
snippet.description:
❤ Princess Closet - Reo Kamiyoshi Walkthrough - Chapter One: Decision

❤ If you enjoyed this video please like it, share it and subscribe to my channel! Thank you! ❤

✿ Do you want to see walkthroughs of your favourite games? Fill out this short survey to help me build the channel with the right content! Thank you!

https://surveynuts.com/surveys/take?id=142460&c=3249797537FDPD

The video contains only the raw story, I cut out the loading time and the ads aswell. If you think my pace is too slow (or too fast), please let me know in the comment section!

---------------------------------------------

"With no real ambition in life, you luck out and manage to get a job at a large company. Although not overwhelmingly dissatisfied, you are bored by the daily, unchanging routine work. And you find yourself wondering, "Am I okay with the way things are?" Your only small relief from all of this is fashion.

That is, until the day that "Leo," the up-and-coming fashion brand designer, suddenly appears in front of you. At that moment, you never suspected that your encounter with him would change your life drastically... "Fashion and romance will change my life." A dating sim game for girls who want to experience heart-throbbing romance, while enjoying fashion!"

❤ Download Princess Closet from the Google Play Store for free!

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.ciagram.pclosetforeign&hl=hu

---------------------------------------------

Otome Walkthroughs is a channel dedicated to share walkthroughs and guides about free to play otome games. I do not own the rights to Princess Closet). All the rights belong to the creators of Princess Closet (Ciagram Ltd.)
